# World Explorer 3D

A simple 3D world exploration game built with vanilla JavaScript and Canvas API.

## Features
- **Free movement** with W/A/S/D keys
- **Looking around** with arrow keys
- **Isometric 3D projection** of world objects
- **Distance-based rendering** with painter's algorithm
- **Real-time position and angle tracking**

## Controls
- **W** - Move forward
- **S** - Move backward
- **A** - Strafe left
- **D** - Strafe right
- **Left Arrow** - Turn left
- **Right Arrow** - Turn right

## Play Online
Visit: https://voidtech10.github.io/world_explorer_3d

## How It Works
The game uses a simple isometric projection to render 3D objects on a 2D canvas. Objects are sorted by distance from the player and rendered back-to-front using the painter's algorithm. The movement system supports both rotation and strafing for full 2D navigation.

